MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2006-Cab.(ii)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 24th October, 2006
2 Kartika, 1928 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 24th October,
2006:-
i)
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the offices of the
Minister of External Affairs and the Minister of Labour and
Employment;
Shri Pranab Mukherjee relinquished the office of the Minister of
Defence and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
External Affairs;
ii)
Shri A.K. Antony assumed the charge of the office of the Minister
of Defence;
iv)
Shri Mani Shankar Aiyar assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of Development of North Eastern region. He will continue
to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Panchayati Raj
and Minister of Youth Affairs & Sports;
Shri P.R. Kyndiah relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Development of North Eastern Region.
v)
Shri Oscar Fernandes, the Minister of State (Independent Charge)
Without Portfolio assumed the charge of the office of the Minister
of State (Independent charge) of the Ministry of Labour and
Employment;
vi)
vii)
Shri Chandra Sekhar Sahu relinquished the charge of the office of
the Minister of State in the Ministry of Labour and Employment
and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Rural Development;
Shri Jay Prakash Narayan Yadav assumed the charge of the
office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of Water Resources;
vii)
ix)
Shri M.H. Ambareesh assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Information and Broadcasting;
(K.L. Sharma)
